{
  "texts": [
    "The fine-tuning and evaluation processes in our experiments are conducted using the Hugging-Face's transformers (Wolf et al., 2020a) framework on a single node instance with 8 Nvidia A100 GPUs.",
    "Accuracy performance is evaluated at three different stages of the PTQ-QLoRA integration: 1.",
    "16-bit fully fined-tuned model after SFT, noted as SFT-16bit",
    "4-bit quantized model on top of SFT, noted as PTQ-{quant-method}-4bit",
    "A LoRA with the 4-bit quantized model after the QLoRA fine-tuning, noted as PTQ-{quant-method}-4bit+QLoRA"
  ]
}